                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": "The fighter drinks his <i>potions of bear\u2019s endurance </i>and <i>cat\u2019s grace</i>, plus his <i>potion of enlarge person </i>if he has time."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": "The fighter gets many foes within reach, then makes a Whirlwind Attack to hit them all, using Lunge if he can get a few more. He tries to sunder shields to get a free attack with Greater Sunder."
            },
